" By migrating the segmented sieve into GPU L1 shared memory and coupling it with a decentralised, lock-free work-stealing pool, we decouple the GPU computation from the CPU completely","A Lock-Free, Fully GPU-Resident Architecture for the Verification of Goldbach’s Conjecture"
